&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Control Room: &lt;/strong&gt;Oversight of the day to day operations and administration of the Security Department. To manage and operate the security system including access control, CCTV and alarm systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contract Security Team Management&lt;/strong&gt;: The supervision and maintenance of consistently high-performance standards; to ensure the Company’s requirements are met, both in Security and Client Service areas. Liaising regularly with the Contract Security Team to identify and resolve any issues; arrange and monitor bookings as required; check and monitor invoices and expenses.&lt;/li&gt;
