&lt;li&gt;Cultivate strong relationships with new and existing clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage in company philosophy/niche and goals, via broader business development projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Sotheby’s Wine during select networking and tasting events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the development of marketing content including tailored offers, tasting notes, and content for email, website, and social media campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support retail team by working on the sales floor of the retail store&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
