&lt;p&gt;The Managing Director, China, holds executive responsibility for driving sustainable growth via client development and partnerships, while managing all facets of the China business. Reporting to the Managing Director, Asia, this leader fosters collaboration across local, regional, and global teams to cultivate collectors, expand auction and private sales, and ensure operational resilience in a regulated environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Client Development &amp;amp; Partnership-Driven Growth&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Build and deepen relationships with China-based collectors to secure consignments and boost private sales, acting as senior sponsor for personalized client experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Identify new client segments and forge strategic partnerships to accelerate development and originate high-value opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Collaborate with specialists, category leaders, regional, and global teams to optimize cross-category sales and align on priorities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Network Connectivity &amp;amp; Global Integration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Cultivate trusted ties with global and regional category heads (e.g., Chinese Works of Art, Jewelry, Contemporary Art) for seamless collaboration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Integrate China clients into Sotheby&#39;s worldwide network to unlock cross-border engagements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN&quot;&gt;Represent Sotheby&#39;s China externally to elevate brand positioning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_xxxmsonormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance, Governance &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Provide strong oversight of regulatory compliance, risk management, and operational excellence within China.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ensure all activities align with local regulations and Sotheby’s global standards and policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Partner with legal, compliance, and operations teams to navigate China’s dynamic regulatory landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
